---
title: Honey Beef & Haloumi Gyros  with Garlic Yoghurt & Oven-Baked Fries
description: A beloved dish from the Mediterranean is hitting your table tonight. Wrap up a bunch of flavours in a toasty flatbread, such as garlic and herb beef, spinach and feta. The serving of baked fries isn’t just a side dish tonight, try adding a few to the gyros to bring everything together.
